title: Nation's top linebacker Lyndell Wilson presented with Under Armour All-American jersey
text:
Nation's top linebacker Lyndell Wilson presented with Under Armour All-American jersey Tools 
Story Created: Oct 14, 2015 at 6:12 PM CDT 
Montgomery, AL - Under Armour presented five-star linebacker Lyndell Wilson with his All-American jersey on Wednesday. 
The Carver High School standout is the first Under Armour All-American in school history. Wilson will play in the Under Armour All-Star game and the Alabama - Mississippi All-Star game. 
Wilson is the nation's top linebacker, and has more than 35 scholarship offers. Wilson narrowed his choices to eight two weeks ago.
